plans.goal:
(:goal
        (exists (?a - agent)
        (exists (?r - receptacle)
        (exists (?o - object)
        (exists (?ot - object)
        (exists (?l - location)
            (and 
                (objectType ?ot FloorLampType)
                (toggleable ?ot)
                (isToggled ?ot) 
                (objectAtLocation ?ot ?l)
                (atLocation ?a ?l)
                (objectType ?o RemoteControlType)
                (holds ?a ?o)
            )
    ))))))
